{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "hc-clinic-staff-conversation-hospital-llc",
    "category": "pro",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LlC-Trk54Zg",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What's wrong with you, John?",
      "zh": "你怎麼了，約翰？",
      "ja": "ジョン、どうしたの？",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You look sick.",
      "zh": "你看起來病了。",
      "ja": "具合が悪そうだね。",
      "time": "00:00:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't know what is wrong with me.",
      "zh": "我不知道我怎麼了。",
      "ja": "自分でも何が悪いのかわからない。",
      "time": "00:00:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:00:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't you have a cold?",
      "zh": "你是不是感冒了？",
      "ja": "風邪じゃないの？",
      "time": "00:00:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What is your symptom?",
      "zh": "你的症狀是什麼？",
      "ja": "症状は何？",
      "time": "00:00:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Um...",
      "zh": "嗯……",
      "ja": "えっと…",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I was shivering and it was cold last night.",
      "zh": "我昨晚發抖，覺得很冷。",
      "ja": "昨夜は震えて寒かった。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think I have a headache too.",
      "zh": "我覺得我也頭痛。",
      "ja": "頭痛もあると思う。",
      "time": "00:00:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I also snuffle and cough too.",
      "zh": "我還有鼻塞和咳嗽。",
      "ja": "鼻づまりと咳もある。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I'm so tired.",
      "zh": "而且我很累。",
      "ja": "それにすごく疲れている。",
      "time": "00:00:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh my goodness!",
      "zh": "天啊！",
      "ja": "まあ！",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm pretty sure you have a cold.",
      "zh": "我很確定你感冒了。",
      "ja": "きっと風邪をひいているよ。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's not even winter yet.",
      "zh": "現在還不是冬天呢。",
      "ja": "まだ冬じゃないのに。",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And the weather is warm too.",
      "zh": "天氣也很暖和。",
      "ja": "天気も暖かいのに。",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "John, listen.",
      "zh": "約翰，聽我說。",
      "ja": "ジョン、聞いて。",
      "time": "00:01:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's warm afternoon.",
      "zh": "現在是溫暖的下午。",
      "ja": "暖かい午後だよ。",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But what about in morning?",
      "zh": "但早上呢？",
      "ja": "でも朝はどう？",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Isn't it cold?",
      "zh": "不是很冷嗎？",
      "ja": "寒くない？",
      "time": "00:01:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's easy to catch a cold during the change of seasons.",
      "zh": "換季時很容易感冒。",
      "ja": "季節の変わり目は風邪をひきやすいよ。",
      "time": "00:01:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I did not know that.",
      "zh": "我不知道這點。",
      "ja": "知らなかった。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I thought I only catch a cold during the winter.",
      "zh": "我以為只有冬天才會感冒。",
      "ja": "風邪は冬だけだと思ってた。",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You should drink lots of warm water and eat foods for vitamins.",
      "zh": "你應該多喝溫水，多吃含維他命的食物。",
      "ja": "たくさん温かい水を飲んで、ビタミンのある食べ物を食べなさい。",
      "time": "00:01:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "If you are not cured, you need to go to a hospital.",
      "zh": "如果沒好轉，你需要去醫院。",
      "ja": "治らなければ病院に行く必要があるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah, I should.",
      "zh": "是啊，我應該去。",
      "ja": "うん、そうするべきだね。",
      "time": "00:01:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "When is the science homework due?",
      "zh": "科學作業什麼時候交？",
      "ja": "理科の宿題はいつまで？",
      "time": "00:01:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ouch!",
      "zh": "哎呀！",
      "ja": "痛っ！",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What's wrong?",
      "zh": "怎麼了？",
      "ja": "どうしたの？",
      "time": "00:01:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It hurts so much.",
      "zh": "好痛。",
      "ja": "すごく痛い。",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm scared that this could be a serious one.",
      "zh": "我怕這可能是嚴重的。",
      "ja": "これが重症かもしれなくて怖い。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Where?",
      "zh": "哪裡？",
      "ja": "どこ？",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Did you get hurt?",
      "zh": "你受傷了嗎？",
      "ja": "怪我したの？",
      "time": "00:02:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look at this.",
      "zh": "看這個。",
      "ja": "これを見て。",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "John, I have a bandage.",
      "zh": "約翰，我有繃帶。",
      "ja": "ジョン、包帯があるよ。",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't be a crybaby.",
      "zh": "別哭哭啼啼的。",
      "ja": "泣き虫にならないで。",
      "time": "00:02:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "At two.",
      "zh": "兩點鐘。",
      "ja": "2時に。",
      "time": "00:02:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oops.",
      "zh": "哎呀。",
      "ja": "おっと。",
      "time": "00:02:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What's wrong with you?",
      "zh": "你怎麼了？",
      "ja": "どうしたの？",
      "time": "00:02:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no.",
      "zh": "糟了。",
      "ja": "やばい。",
      "time": "00:02:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think I caught a cold from you.",
      "zh": "我想我被你傳染感冒了。",
      "ja": "君から風邪をうつされたみたい。",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "At two.",
      "zh": "兩點鐘。",
      "ja": "2時に。",
      "time": "00:02:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's role play.",
      "zh": "我們來角色扮演吧。",
      "ja": "ロールプレイをしよう。",
      "time": "00:02:39"
    }
  ]
}